        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 5. Leitoscoloplos fragilis (Verrill, 1873). Juveniles: A, 28-setiger juvenile, dorsolateral view; B, 32-setiger juvenile, dorsolateral view; C, 40-setiger juvenile, lateral view; D, same, abdominal setiger with interramal cirrus; E, far posterior setigers, lateral view; F, anterior and posterior ends, with pygidium. A (MCZ 161584); B (MCZ 161567). All stained with Shirlastain A." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4544908/files/figure.png" .

